Package com.ringcentral.definitions

Class PerformanceCallsAdditionalFilters

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ringcentral.definitions.PerformanceCallsAdditionalFilters
  • public class PerformanceCallsAdditionalFilters
extends java.lang.Object
    Optional filters that limit the scope of calls to be aggregated. Multiple values can be joined via 'AND'

    • Field Detail

      • direction

        public java.lang.String direction
        Specifies whether the call was inbound or outbound relative to the scope specified in grouping object. Not applicable to internal calls with company scope (when grouping is not specified) Enum: Inbound, Outbound

      • origin

        public java.lang.String origin
        Specifies whether an external party was present in the initial segment of the call Enum: Internal, External

      • callResponse

        public java.lang.String callResponse
        Aggregation of calls by the first response Enum: Answered, NotAnswered, Connected, NotConnected

      • callType

        public java.lang.String[] callType
        List of call response types. This filter allows to get aggregation of calls based on how the call started from the callee perspective. Multiple values can be joined via 'OR'. If the call is outbound relative to the grouping scope, `callType` is Outbound Enum: Direct, Outbound, ParkRetrieval, FromQueue, Transferred

      • callResult

        public java.lang.String[] callResult
        Aggregation of calls by the nature of call result. Multiple values can be joined via 'OR' Enum: Completed, Abandoned, VoiceMail, Unknown, Missed, Accepted

      • callSegments

        public CallSegmentFilter[] callSegments
        Aggregation of calls by presence of specific segment. Multiple values can be joined via 'OR'

      • callActions

        public CallPerformanceActionInfo[] callActions
        Aggregation of calls by presence of specific action (joined via OR)

      • companyHours

        public java.lang.String companyHours
        Aggregation of calls by company business hours or after hours. Enum: BusinessHours, AfterHours

      • callDuration

        public PerformanceCallsFilterByLength callDuration

      • timeSpent

        public PerformanceCallsFilterTimeSpentByMailbox timeSpent

      • callerExtensionIds

        public java.lang.String[] callerExtensionIds
        List of extension identifiers from which the users specified in 'groupBy' received calls. Multiple values can be joined via 'OR'

      • calledExtensionIds

        public java.lang.String[] calledExtensionIds
        List of extension identifiers to which the users specified in 'groupBy' placed calls. Multiple values can be joined via 'OR'

      • calledNumbers

        public java.lang.String[] calledNumbers
        Direct numbers the caller dialed. Multiple values can be joined via 'OR'

      • queueSla

        public java.lang.String queueSla
        This filter allows to get aggregation of calls that were either within or out of queue SLA. Only applicable to Queues grouping Enum: InSla, OutSla
